---
title: Caramelised Beef & Capsicum Subs with Sour Cream, Balsamic Salad & Smokey Aioli
description: Big flavour, no fuss! These sublime subs are packed with juicy beef, sweet caramelised onions and a drizzle of smokey aioli, all tucked into a soft roll. It’s a handheld feast that’s messy in the best way!
